						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 7(1/2) <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold and a lamp-stand for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Tirumūlaṭṭānattu-Perumānaḍigaḷ by one <hi rend="bold">Śeruviḍai Ariñjigai.</hi> This is probably a record of <hi rend="bold">Parāntaka I.</hi> (No. 64, <hi rend="italic">Pud. Ins.</hi> Texts).</p>						

						</summary>
